{"tid":1150240,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2018-19 LIHKG香港超級女神聯賽 結果公佈!!","createTime":"2019-05-11T16:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T04:27:57.000Z","uid":92376,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"49aff24d7f1afaf617a7ee6940bd1070ae8a13cc","tid":1150240,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T16:56:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mQzyFpS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FmQzyFpS.png&h=fb1db3e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最終, 李佳芯以102分奪得今屆超級聯賽冠軍,係第一次奪冠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />詳細結果:<br />\n冠軍 李佳芯 102<br />\n亞軍 陳法拉 96<br />\n季軍 朱千雪 87<br />\n來季環球女神冠軍盃分組賽資格<br />\n<br />\n第四名 文詠珊 84<br />\n來季環球女神冠軍盃附加賽資格<br />\n<br />\n總會盃冠軍: 苟芸慧<br />\n<br />\n降班或去向未明:<br />\n第16名: 麥明詩 12<br />\n第17名: 陳穎欣@SG 6<br />\n第18名: 杜小喬 3<br />\n<br />\n由於上述三人雖身處降班區但全季分數未達19分之法許降班線<br />\n故需要參與稍後舉行既季尾清算大會,由會員決定來季前途為降班或直接取消下季資格<br />\n<br />\n來季由冠聯升班:<br />\n1st 劉穎鏇、2nd 朱晨麗<br />\n<br />\n冠聯升班附加賽(賽程待公佈,有消息會喺此post補充)<br />\n四強首回合:<br />\n湯怡(第五名) Vs 岑麗香(第四名)<br />\n莊錠欣(第六名) Vs 林泳淘(第三名)<br />\n<br />\n四強次回合:<br />\n岑麗香(第四名) Vs 湯怡(第五名)<br />\n林泳淘(第三名) Vs 莊錠欣(第六名)<br />\n<br />\n決賽勝方將獲最後一個升班名額<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝各位巴打絲打今季一直既支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外LIHKG香港女神聯賽 來季(19-20)新加入女神提名大會 亦已經開始左架啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1097889\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1097889</a><br />\n有心水既話記得提名,因為錯過咗就要再等下季架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9343f95bfbfd3e86de9a8f09fd1526ce03ce6ade","tid":1150240,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T17:04:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b41c53515befdea2f8cb31531bdfede11bd20c57","tid":1150240,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9343f95bfbfd3e86de9a8f09fd1526ce03ce6ade","tid":1150240,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T17:04:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T17:07:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170e349b6cc3027782b87c9d975718c492797fce","tid":1150240,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T17:19:34.000Z","msg":"睇錯咗文詠珊做 Theresa May <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def8e08862cb4d4fc850b964ea81f9d6eca2c5f6","tid":1150240,"uid":15414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T23:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"296d6ff9f1e93fb5941c2b7adf0358bdd3b291b4","tid":1150240,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T15:45:45.000Z","msg":"由於資料需要整理<br />\n清算大會會喺星期四深夜12點即翌日為周五開始 為期至提名大會結束"},{"pid":"938104a5077b0e2ca329098be50f5cacdd82582e","tid":1150240,"uid":245425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:37:47.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3871672fab3d69ec88ec6642bc524a6bd7a5b2","tid":1150240,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T04:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}